456
00:26:41.720 --> 00:26:43.319
Dia sangat tampan.

457
00:26:43.790 --> 00:26:45.020
Benar.

458
00:26:46.690 --> 00:26:47.819
Ayo datang lagi.

459
00:26:47.819 --> 00:26:49.020
Baik.

